Add Cultural Object

 

To add Cultural Object to the Project or Folder use Add Cultural Object action or the Add Cultural Object button available. The action is available only for Projects and Folders.​​​

In a dialog window will be presented with a search engine:

  1. Enter search criteria and select the Search button
  2. Select the Cultural Object(s) that you want to be added
  3. Press the Ok button
